@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gfybkb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(v0) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.17 / v2 + 0.48)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.42 + tmp + 0.51)) * 0.75)
    tmp = 0.14
    v2 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.18 + v1 + 0.82) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
